{"tid":1119963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一去到黃昏就好抑鬱?","createTime":"2019-04-22T10:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T03:39:41.000Z","uid":195337,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"594fc86aa37900a61bbebe4755b635abd49300e6","tid":1119963,"uid":195337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"唔知點解一去到5，6點個心就好嗡<br />\n個天半光不黑搞到個人好憂鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人話覺得黃昏好靚好浪漫<br />\n我就一定要搵個室內地方最好見唔到街嘅<br />\n但一去到夜晚同早上中午就好好多<br />\n想知有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075c9a0efeea7d4bd5a5c9868818fb43475dd9e3","tid":1119963,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，黃昏個人唔係好想郁，冇乜精神"},{"pid":"264203e104b69c9b51ef01e7a565b4d8a42497b1","tid":1119963,"uid":48350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"放假到黃昏就會覺得又無左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工到黃昏就諗今晚又要OT幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624bac7a6323c797e91e88ba6a9afa274827aee5","tid":1119963,"uid":195337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"264203e104b69c9b51ef01e7a565b4d8a42497b1","tid":1119963,"uid":48350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"放假到黃昏就會覺得又無左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工到黃昏就諗今晚又要OT幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"係一日完結嘅先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d059add4aa137a27ca99820a3412b28f7188a8","tid":1119963,"uid":85934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"好憎4-7呢段時間"},{"pid":"127e1aa35ee67ac1aef68c128235b5cb63492b